enum VrProperty
 

Enumerator:
IsolatedWordRecognition  asr engine provides isolated word recognizer for speaker dependant / speaker independant recognition; in speaker dependant recognition RejectionValue in AsrRecResult_t can be used.
ConnectedWordRecognition  asr engine provides isolated word recognizer for speaker dependant / speaker independant recognition; in speaker dependant recognition
SpeakerDependentTraining  asr engine provides speaker dependant training
G2ATraining  asr engine provides G2A functions that allow to produce references from written character strings
SpeakerAdaption  asr engine provides speaker adaptation functions, that can be used to improve given references in order to get higher recognition rates in (e.g.) connected word recognition; the adaptation process works like that: the user talks some predefined words into the mobile; during that procedure the user voice is recorded and used to adapt the references that match the spoken words, i.e. the procedure is very similar to a normal (connected word) recognition.
